		 <div class="float-right">
			<h6 style="margin-left:75px;">Characteristics</h6>
			<p style="margin-left:75px;">

			Mass: 6.417 x 10^23 kg <br>
			Diameter: 6,779 km  <br>
			Density: 3.934 g/cm^3 <br> 
			Temperature: Low: -226 &#176;F | <br> Average: -82 &#176;F | High: 95 &#176;F <br>
			Orbital Period: 686.971 Earth Days <br>
			Average distance from Sun: 1.5 AU <br>


			</p>
